#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:166
msgid ""
"edit the :ref:`Cols <building_blocks/cols>` and :ref:`Visibility "
"<building_blocks/visibility>` features in the :guilabel:`Customize` tab of "
